1
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:29,000
You...

2
00:00:29,719 --> 00:00:31,239
It's all your fault!

3
00:00:31,960 --> 00:00:33,920
My future, everything I worked for,

4
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:34,920
has been ruined in an instant!

5
00:00:35,560 --> 00:00:37,079
You thought you were saving lives,

6
00:00:37,759 --> 00:00:40,119
but you didn't realize the danger of your words!

7
00:00:44,039 --> 00:00:44,200
Qingdai!

8
00:00:46,479 --> 00:00:47,079
Qingdai!

9
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:48,560
Qingdai!

10
00:00:49,119 --> 00:00:49,679
Qingdai!

11
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,520
Go get all the healers in the city!

12
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,159
Xiao,

13
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:09,000
Yun,

14
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:09,599
Zhou...

15
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:11,519
Accident, accident.

16
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:12,599
It really was an accident.

17
00:01:12,719 --> 00:01:13,640
When is it not an accident?

18
00:01:14,079 --> 00:01:15,200
Look what I brought you first.

19
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:16,640
Take a look.

20
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:19,799
Zhou Yi.

21
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,359
The school order says,

22
00:01:22,799 --> 00:01:23,680
women's studies

23
00:01:24,239 --> 00:01:25,599
should be confined to the home.

24
00:01:25,879 --> 00:01:26,519
Yet you

25
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:29,599
prefer the obscure and difficult classics.

26
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,359
If men can do it,

27
00:01:31,719 --> 00:01:32,760
why can't women?

28
00:01:33,319 --> 00:01:34,120
Not only do I want to learn,

29
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:36,200
I also want to master the classics,

30
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:37,200
laws,

31
00:01:37,359 --> 00:01:38,040
and arithmetic.

32
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,560
In short,

33
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:41,640
I won't fall behind in any field.

34
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,079
Good.

35
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,439
Qingdai,

36
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:49,319
my father is here.

37
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,000
You should go.

38
00:01:50,239 --> 00:01:51,079
Don't let him see you.

39
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:52,840
[You're still as stubborn as ever,]

40
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,799
[but between us,]

41
00:01:58,280 --> 00:02:00,239
[we're not as reckless as we used to be.]

42
00:02:09,719 --> 00:02:10,599
You're awake.

43
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:12,240
Don't you see?

44
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,319
You've been unconscious for three days.

45
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:22,879
Fortunately, the dagger

46
00:02:23,439 --> 00:02:24,319
didn't hit your vital organs.

47
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:25,960
But you need to rest for a month.

48
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,400
I can do it myself.

49
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:40,360
Here.

50
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:44,680
I have to go.

51
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:48,520
Mrs. Shen is waiting for me to give her an acupuncture.

52
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,560
The clinic can't run without me.

53
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,400
How can I just lie here

54
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,240
and rest?

55
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:00,240
There are millions of doctors in the world.

56
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:01,840
If you don't take care of yourself,

57
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,199
I might as well close the clinic myself.

58
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:04,960
You...

59
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:06,800
Xinyue,

60
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,360
is it convenient to come in?

61
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,400
Come in quickly.

62
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:12,479
Sister Su.

63
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:13,560
Yan Ge.

64
00:03:19,439 --> 00:03:20,039
Xinyue,

65
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:23,599
why is he angry?

66
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:24,800
I don't know either.

67
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:29,000
Is it because you don't cherish yourself

68
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,520
that he is so angry?

69
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:33,960
Whether he is angry or not,

70
00:03:34,039 --> 00:03:35,039
it has nothing to do with me.

71
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,319
Just listen to him this time.

72
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:39,319
We two can take care of the clinic.

73
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,560
Now you are like this,

74
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:43,120
you can't even hold the needle steadily.

75
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:45,479
How can you give a needle to the wife of the Minister?

76
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,400
Sister Su,

77
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,560
why are you siding with him?

78
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:50,560
I'm not.

79
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,159
[She's still alive.]

80
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:56,520
[Xiao Jingyi carried her all the way back.]

81
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:03,719
Getting more sun

82
00:04:04,159 --> 00:04:04,879
will help you recover.

83
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,079
I can do it myself.

84
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:17,279
You don't have to.

85
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,800
Now that you're home safely,

86
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,160
from now on,

87
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,079
don't leave my sight again.

88
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:36,720
Home?

89
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:44,800
It's hot.

90
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,319
Okay.

91
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:55,439
Here.

92
00:04:58,519 --> 00:04:59,600
It's cooled down.

93
00:05:15,279 --> 00:05:16,360
You should get some rest.

94
00:05:17,639 --> 00:05:18,160
Keep an eye on her.

95
00:05:19,439 --> 00:05:19,839
Yes.

96
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,720
Did your master take the wrong medicine?

97
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:29,040
You don't know,

98
00:05:29,519 --> 00:05:31,800
he has been watching over you for three days and nights,

99
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,079
not sleeping even for a moment.

100
00:05:33,439 --> 00:05:34,319
Look at the medicine,

101
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:36,040
he even tested the temperature himself

102
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:36,879
before feeding it to you.

103
00:05:37,959 --> 00:05:39,959
He has always been the most aloof and self-contained,

104
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,680
never allowing emotions to be stirred for anyone.

105
00:05:42,199 --> 00:05:43,399
If it weren't for you,

106
00:05:44,439 --> 00:05:46,759
how could he let go of old grudges?

107
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:51,839
After I broke my promise,

108
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,319
I heard

109
00:05:55,199 --> 00:05:56,360
he was in danger.

110
00:05:57,319 --> 00:05:57,800
Yes.

111
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,240
That day,

112
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,120
he waited for you all day

113
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:02,560
by the Qujiang Pool.

114
00:06:03,439 --> 00:06:04,959
Then he fell into the water.

115
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:06,800
Since then,

116
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,720
he's been like a different person.

117
00:06:10,079 --> 00:06:12,560
You should take care of him.

118
00:06:15,519 --> 00:06:17,120
I asked you to look after her,

119
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,839
not to be a storyteller.

120
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:20,120
Am I right, Nong?

121
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,160
Yes.

122
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:29,519
Take a nap.

123
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:43,920
Sister Su,

124
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:47,040
Xinyue won't be back soon.

125
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,399
How about

126
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,279
we find a doctor to deal with it?

127
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:52,160
That will ease Xinyue's burden.

128
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:57,000
Where can you find another female doctor

129
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,800
who can treat leukorrhea?

130
00:07:00,439 --> 00:07:01,839
If you can't find a female doctor,

131
00:07:02,439 --> 00:07:03,560
can't a male doctor do?

132
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,800
A woman's illness is a private matter.

133
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:09,120
How can we let a man examine her?

134
00:07:10,439 --> 00:07:13,439
For some common illnesses, close examination isn't necessary.

135
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,519
If the Women's clinic stops treating,

136
00:07:16,079 --> 00:07:18,319
what will happen to those women

137
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:19,720
who have been waiting for medical help?

138
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,600
Even if it's a man,

139
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,639
as long as he is respectful,

140
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,720
and skilled,

141
00:07:25,279 --> 00:07:26,319
what's the problem?

142
00:07:28,279 --> 00:07:31,160
We should ask Xin Yue's opinion.

143
00:07:35,439 --> 00:07:36,480
If a healer comes,

144
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:38,439
ask him three questions.

145
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:05,839
Why are your hands so cold?

146
00:08:17,319 --> 00:08:18,399
These male healers...

147
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,160
If a woman is sick,

148
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,600
the husband's life comes first.

149
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,399
She's dying,

150
00:08:23,399 --> 00:08:24,720
and you're still talking about that?

151
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,839
If the suffering in this world

152
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:27,279
is all because of the constraints of propriety,

153
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,839
then it's no different from standing by and watching someone die.

154
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,159
Please sit.

155
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,080
If you encounter a woman

156
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,120
whose menstrual cycle is irregular,

157
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,360
either early or late,

158
00:08:55,919 --> 00:08:57,559
accompanied by cold and painful lower back and abdomen,

159
00:08:57,759 --> 00:08:59,279
you must first determine the diagnosis,

160
00:09:00,279 --> 00:09:00,600
Then,

161
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,039
what method should be used?

162
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:04,000
If it's due to cold stagnation and blood stasis,

163
00:09:04,679 --> 00:09:06,799
you can use modified Warming the Uterus Decoction to warm the uterus,

164
00:09:06,799 --> 00:09:07,879
dispel cold, and promote blood circulation.

165
00:09:08,559 --> 00:09:09,279
If there's also weakness,

166
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,559
add Astragalus to tonify qi

167
00:09:10,879 --> 00:09:12,120
and assist the flow of qi and blood.

168
00:09:12,559 --> 00:09:13,919
A woman in her fourth month of pregnancy

169
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:16,759
is experiencing lower abdominal pain and is afraid to tell her family.

170
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:17,919
How should she be comforted

171
00:09:18,159 --> 00:09:19,240
How should you diagnose her?

172
00:09:19,519 --> 00:09:20,600
It's likely due to the growing fetus

173
00:09:20,879 --> 00:09:21,919
causing slight stagnation of qi and blood.

174
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,080
It's not an emergency.

175
00:09:23,879 --> 00:09:24,480
When taking the pulse,

176
00:09:24,799 --> 00:09:25,879
use a silk-covered pulse cushion.

177
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,480
Ask about her daily life and diet.

178
00:09:27,919 --> 00:09:28,759
Examine the tongue coating

179
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:29,759
and observe her complexion.

180
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:34,240
If you diagnose the fetus as unsettled,

181
00:09:34,759 --> 00:09:36,480
how would you communicate with her family?

182
00:09:37,759 --> 00:09:39,240
Just say the fetus is slightly unstable,

183
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:40,679
which is common during pregnancy.

184
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,639
It might be due to recent fatigue

185
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,440
or getting cold.

186
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,320
Prescribe a tonic for the fetus

187
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:46,679
and advise bed rest.

188
00:09:51,559 --> 00:09:52,960
Welcome to the Women's Clinic.

189
00:09:53,759 --> 00:09:55,440
May I ask your name?

190
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:55,879
Join?

191
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:57,159
Join

192
00:09:57,679 --> 00:09:58,639
the Women's Clinic?

193
00:09:59,559 --> 00:09:59,960
You...

194
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,679
Didn't you come to apply?

195
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,879
I'm Si Xiangting.

196
00:10:08,639 --> 00:10:09,879
My father took bribes

197
00:10:10,159 --> 00:10:11,120
and caused trouble at Ren'an Hall.

198
00:10:11,879 --> 00:10:13,360
He even accused Madam Yin of poor skills

199
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:15,240
and forced her to test the medicine.

200
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:16,720
It was truly unconscionable.

201
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:18,200
I was studying abroad and unaware.

202
00:10:18,519 --> 00:10:19,240
I just found out recently.

203
00:10:19,799 --> 00:10:20,240
I came

204
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,240
to apologize.

205
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:24,639
You answered so thoroughly.

206
00:10:25,159 --> 00:10:26,000
Because you asked me.

207
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:27,840
You told me to sit,

208
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,279
didn't you?

209
00:10:29,639 --> 00:10:29,840
I...

210
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,120
[Is he truly foolishly adorable,]

211
00:10:35,399 --> 00:10:38,240
[or just playing dumb?]

212
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:40,679
Unfortunately,

213
00:10:41,559 --> 00:10:42,360
I don't know...

214
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,080
I'd like to stay.

215
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,480
That's great.

216
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:51,679
We'll treat you with the utmost sincerity.

217
00:10:58,240 --> 00:11:01,120
[The menstrual cycle ranges from 3 months]

218
00:11:01,679 --> 00:11:03,240
[to 10 days, accompanied by breast pain.]

219
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,879
[Women in Jiangnan work hard,]

220
00:11:06,279 --> 00:11:07,080
[with good blood circulation.]

221
00:11:07,679 --> 00:11:08,720
[They can take Xiaoyao Powder]

222
00:11:09,039 --> 00:11:09,799
[to soothe the liver and dispel depression.]

223
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:13,679
[But women in Chang'an live in large houses,]

224
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:15,480
[though they are not hungry or cold,]

225
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,879
they suffer from internal heat.

226
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,799
We need to use 30 grams of saffron,

227
00:11:20,279 --> 00:11:21,919
which clears heat and cools the blood,

228
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,440
and add ligustrum fruits

229
00:11:23,799 --> 00:11:24,480
to nourish the liver and kidneys.

230
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:29,120
You're truly a knowledgeable healer.

231
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:30,240
Brilliant!

232
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,720
I just love to travel

233
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:33,000
and have learned various things.

234
00:11:33,919 --> 00:11:36,679
I didn't expect Yan Ge to be so eager to learn.

235
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,120
My lady,

236
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,799
how are you?

237
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:50,279
You...

238
00:11:53,039 --> 00:11:53,759
What are you doing?

239
00:11:54,559 --> 00:11:55,440
Let go!

240
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:56,320
What are you doing?

241
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:56,559
Step back!

242
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:59,080
I won't go back with you.

243
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,240
I want a divorce.

244
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:01,879
Divorce?

245
00:12:03,759 --> 00:12:05,559
Do you know who you are?

246
00:12:06,559 --> 00:12:09,120
You can't take off the clothes of the Matriarch.

247
00:12:09,559 --> 00:12:11,240
If I don't take you back today,

248
00:12:11,559 --> 00:12:12,279
tomorrow,

249
00:12:12,799 --> 00:12:14,799
I'll be the laughingstock of Chang'an.

250
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:17,159
Don't you ever touch me again.

251
00:12:17,399 --> 00:12:18,120
I'd rather die

252
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,360
than go back to that hell with you.

253
00:12:20,799 --> 00:12:21,360
If you dare,

254
00:12:21,799 --> 00:12:23,039
just kill me.

255
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:24,840
Fine,

256
00:12:25,919 --> 00:12:27,440
then I'll smash your clinic.

257
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,279
Let's see how you'll keep your arrogance.

258
00:12:29,799 --> 00:12:30,559
Do it!

259
00:12:31,159 --> 00:12:31,639
Smash it!

260
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:32,960
No!

261
00:12:36,919 --> 00:12:37,399
No!

262
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:50,519
Stop!

263
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:52,919
How dare you

264
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,559
do this in front of the Emperor?

265
00:12:54,879 --> 00:12:55,879
Do you think Chang'an is lawless?

266
00:12:55,879 --> 00:12:56,320
Nonsense!

267
00:12:56,559 --> 00:12:56,960
Beat him!

268
00:13:02,519 --> 00:13:03,320
Stop!

269
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,000
Stop!

270
00:13:04,519 --> 00:13:05,279
Don't hurt him!

271
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:06,879
Stop!

272
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:07,440
Stop!

273
00:13:07,879 --> 00:13:08,240
Enough!

274
00:13:09,559 --> 00:13:10,480
I'll go with you.

275
00:13:10,799 --> 00:13:11,799
No, Su!

276
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,559
He's cruel and vicious.

277
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:14,960
Going with him now

278
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,320
is like walking into a trap!

279
00:13:16,879 --> 00:13:18,200
I almost forgot about you.

280
00:13:18,919 --> 00:13:20,679
You ambushed me in the alley last time.

281
00:13:21,159 --> 00:13:22,159
Take both of them away.

282
00:13:24,879 --> 00:13:25,080
Let's go.

283
00:13:25,519 --> 00:13:25,840
You...

284
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:26,720
You...

285
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:30,480
Slow down.

286
00:13:50,039 --> 00:13:50,559
Yunzhou,

287
00:13:52,039 --> 00:13:53,120
could you do me a favor?

288
00:13:53,879 --> 00:13:54,360
Okay.

289
00:13:57,519 --> 00:13:58,919
You are injured.

290
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:00,159
No need to be polite.

291
00:14:00,639 --> 00:14:01,159
My Lady,

292
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:03,600
I have a request.

293
00:14:03,879 --> 00:14:04,919
Go ahead.

294
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:09,000
Shen Yuan destroyed my clinic

295
00:14:09,679 --> 00:14:12,200
and took my friends, Su and Yan Ge.

296
00:14:12,639 --> 00:14:14,240
Please help me.

297
00:14:15,559 --> 00:14:16,200
This involves

298
00:14:16,679 --> 00:14:18,159
many officials.

299
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,679
Why should I help you?

300
00:14:21,159 --> 00:14:22,080
If I say

301
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:24,799
I can help you deal with the poisoner,

302
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:25,679
My Lady,

303
00:14:26,039 --> 00:14:27,000
would you be willing to help?

304
00:14:30,919 --> 00:14:32,279
Tell me,

305
00:14:32,759 --> 00:14:34,039
how can this dagger

306
00:14:34,559 --> 00:14:36,480
reveal the truth?

307
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:37,879
My Lady,

308
00:14:38,879 --> 00:14:40,159
just wait for Zhou Xiaoning to arrive,

309
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:41,559
and the truth will be revealed.

310
00:14:53,399 --> 00:14:54,120
Do you recognize

311
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,120
this dagger?

312
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:58,799
I've never seen this dagger before.

313
00:14:59,039 --> 00:15:01,000
The design on this dagger

314
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:03,600
is a unique gilding technique from Jiangnan.

315
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:06,919
There are only a few families in Chang'an

316
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,759
that can afford it.

317
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,279
I remember

318
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:14,200
last year on your birthday,

319
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:16,399
my lord specially ordered

320
00:15:16,399 --> 00:15:17,519
a custom iron weapon for you.

321
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:20,840
It was a dagger, if I recall correctly.

322
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:22,639
My Lady,

323
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:23,799
you wronged me.

324
00:15:23,799 --> 00:15:24,679
It's not me.

325
00:15:25,639 --> 00:15:26,360
This dagger...

326
00:15:27,279 --> 00:15:29,159
I lost it for days.

327
00:15:30,039 --> 00:15:31,960
You just said it's not yours,

328
00:15:32,159 --> 00:15:33,159
and now you say you lost it.

329
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:36,159
Why don't you bring your maid here?

330
00:15:36,559 --> 00:15:39,080
Why did you want to kill me?
